<br>
Brute wizard (fast exp method, but dangerous): Quaff a sow potion. Nuke run Nuke run Nuke run<br>
<br>
Suicidal Wizard (Holy moly lots of experience, but death will happen, expect it): Get your stamina as high as possible. Quaff a sow potion, Apply your diamond skin (or whichever), hit everything you can find and create a massive train. Personal AOE, run like heck - Reapply diamond skin (and probably bind wounds), Personal AOE, run like heck (Wise to have a healer with you if you do this method).<br>
<br>
Abusive wizard: Quaff a sow potion. smack mob 1, mob 2, mob 3, and mob 4, AOE run AOE run AOE run<br>
<br>
Standard Wizard: Root, BOF, Nuke, break root, Root, Nuke, break root, Nuke<br>
<br>
Thrifty Wizard: Quaff a sow potion. BOF mob 1, run, BOF mob 2, run, BOF mob 3, run, BOF mob 4, run and center, let them group. BOF all 4, run, AOE, run, AOE, run, AOE, run..etc<br>
<br>
Crafty Wizard: Get your first group of mobs: Quaff a sow potion. BOF mob 1, run, BOF mob 2, run, BOF mob 3, run, BOF mob 4, run and center, let them group. BOF all 4, run ====Repeat 3 times to create 3 groups of 4 (Make sure you reapply BOF or Atols on each group whenever you get to the last step). AOE group 1, sit, run, AOE group 2, sit, run, AOE group 3, sit, run. Reapply BOF on all 3 groups then repeat.<br>
Having a horse is almost a must, as you need to sit down to regain your mana (You won't have enough if you don't med a little) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=avonjahl>Avonjahl</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.exoblivion.com/animations/redrad.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 106<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/3/03 8:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=199.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wizard types</span><hr size=1> Neat...I'm brute and abusive....oh wait..that didnt sound right <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rollin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/roll.gif ALT=":rollin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Well you know what I mean!! <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=587800" target="top">Avonjahl Sunstrike</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
